{"tid":329400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"２內地女子甫抵香港　在中環美領事館放爆仗被捕","createTime":"2017-07-20T10:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T19:00:26.000Z","uid":13663,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c04ab19ededbf92d4ed30dea943c19da77ff32f0","tid":329400,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"下午12時許，2名持雙程證今日抵港湖南籍女子，在中環美國駐港領事館門外燒炮仗，現場留下一堆紅色爆仗衣紙及一個被爆至破爛的環保袋，警員接報到場當場將2人拘捕，並帶返警署調查。消息指，有人對內地不滿。<br />\n<br />\n被捕2名女子，分別姓羅（72歲）及姓王（65歲），她們報稱來自湖南省，今日到香港，在港沒有固定居所。警方其後在她們身上檢獲打火機和爆仗的包裝紙。警方現正追查2人動機及爆仗的來源。<br />\n<br />\n美國領事館回應指，事件發生在領事館外的地方，保安員得悉事件後即時通知警方，警方迅速對事件作出跟進，事件現交由香港警方處理。"},{"pid":"7a1574edbd7220abf1a1f2720c11f5219868603d","tid":329400,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"睇黎支那真係怕再有王立軍事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8092c9bd817d3da42a3e9b2ad1403cb6849cc217","tid":329400,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71e82050cda75495d64e7f84cb28befa46dd44c","tid":329400,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:40:21.000Z","msg":"我地湖南人呢 就唔衰得既"},{"pid":"a139ac579e4675c5da9a4edca1a16803911da68b","tid":329400,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:42:31.000Z","msg":"放左炮仗 領事館一定提升保安級別<br />\n想9衝又高左難道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67e2df3f425b8911776465181432bb204321aa3","tid":329400,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T10:43:52.000Z","msg":"對內地不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb92759eb9214068a3ea06d3585f16abf15cdfd","tid":329400,"uid":46454